<H3> <TI>   Shumeyko: Negotiations With Chechnya Unavoidable </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Shumeyko: Negotiations With Chechnya Unavoidable </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0906095994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0714 GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0906095994 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS parliamentary correspondent Lyudmila Yermakova] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 9 TASS -- "The negotiating process with 
Chechnya will have to be conducted," Federation Council Chairman 
Vladimir Shumeyko told journalists today. 
  Shumeyko expressed regret in connection with the act of 
terror against Dzhokhar Dudayev and surmised that "forces which 
do not want stabilisation of relations" are seeking to impede 
the process. 
  He noted that the attitude to the act of terror has changed 
in Chechnya, "which is evidenced by the stripping of some 
individuals of the Chechen citizenship". 

</TEXT>

