<F P=100> Federal Assembly </F>
<H3> <TI>   Yeltsin, Shumeyko Discuss Federation Council </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Yeltsin, Shumeyko Discuss Federation Council </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0906123594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1148 GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0906123594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Moscow June 9 ITAR-TASS -- Russian President Boris 
Yeltsin and Federation Council Chairman Vladimir Shumeyko met in 
the Kremlin today to discuss the effectiveness of work of the 
upper chamber of the Federal Assembly (parliament) of the 
Russian Federation. 
  Shumeyko briefed the president on the results of his tour of 
a number of Latin American countries. 

</TEXT>

