<F P=102>   OW0906061794 Moscow Russian Television and Dubl Networks in 
Russian 0600 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW0906061794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Russian Television and Dubl Networks </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video; from the news segment of </F>
the "Dalniy Vostok" program] 
  [Text] Parliamentary hearings devoted to an analysis of 
the condition and problems of the Russian state border have 
ended. The State Duma Committee for Geopolitics adopted a 
decision to set up a working group of qualified experts to 
comprehensively assess the possibility of concluding a peace 
treaty with Japan, taking into consideration the 1956 
declaration on Shikotan and Habomai. 
  As you know Russia signed this declaration in which the 
turnover of the islands of Shikotan and Habomai to Japan is 
stipulated as a condition for the signing of the peace treaty. 
State Duma deputies do not rule out the possibility of finding 
a compromise version in the territorial dispute with Japan. 

