<DOCNO> FBIS4-39632 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drsov111_a_94032" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-SOV-94-111 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  8 Jun 1994 </DATE1>

