<H3> <TI>   Envoy, Danish Defense Minister Discuss European Security </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Envoy, Danish Defense Minister Discuss European Security </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0806204894 Kiev UNIAR in Ukrainian 1500 GMT 8 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0806204894 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev UNIAR </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Copenhagen, Denmark, 8 Jun -- Ukrainian Ambassador 
to Denmark Konstantin Masik and Danish Defense Minister Hans 
Haekkerup met to address questions of security and stability in 
Europe and cooperation between Ukraine and Denmark within the 
framework of the "Partnership for Peace" program. Mr. Masik 
informed the defense minister of the situation in Crimea and the 
work of the Ukrainian and Russian delegations to settle the 
issue of the Black Sea Fleet. Mssrs Haekkerup and Masik 
exchanged views on the results of the work at the latest NATO 
session and the possibilities of that organization's expansion. 

