  [Text] Baku, 9 June, IRNA -- Iranian ambassador to Baku 
'Ali Asghar Nahavandiyan and Azeri Minister of National Security 
Nariman Imranof on Wednesday explored ways of confronting 
certain elements suspected of disturbing Iranian people residing 
in Azerbaijan. 
