protecting the life and properties of Iranians residing in 
Azerbaijan. 
  He invited his Iranian counterpart 'Ali Fallahiyan to pay an 
official visit to his country and expressed hope that in the 
upcoming visit to Tehran of Azeri President Heydar Aliyev 
agreements on border and security cooperation would be signed by 
the two countries. 

