<H3> <TI>   Zvyahilskyy, U.S. Ambassador Discuss Economic Cooperation </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Zvyahilskyy, U.S. Ambassador Discuss Economic Cooperation </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   WS1006113794 Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network in 
Ukrainian 0500 GMT 10 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> WS1006113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Ukrayinske Radio First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ukrainian Acting Prime Minister Yukhym Zvyahilskyy 
received William Miller, U.S. ambassador extraordinary and 
plenipotentiary to Ukraine. During their conversation, both 
officials discussed the present economic situation in Ukraine 
and cooperation opportunities between our countries. In 
particular, they touched upon U.S. aid regarding the deported 
Crimean people. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

