BFN 

  [Text] President Akayev has sent a message of greetings to 
Russian President Yeltsin. Akayev congratulated Yeltsin on the 
occasion of the anniversary of the declaration of independence 
and stressed that Russia is, will, and should be Kyrgyzstan's 
