<H3> <TI>   Afghanistan Border Situation Remains Tense </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Afghanistan Border Situation Remains Tense </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1306095794 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0924 GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1306095794 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Report by ITAR-TASS correspondent Vladimir Gondusov] </F>
  [Text] Moscow 13 June TASS -- The situation on the 
Tajik-Afghan border remained tense this weekend. An armed band 
made an attempt to cross into Tajikistan from Afghanistan on the 
third sector outpost of the Pyandzh frontier guard detachment on 
Sunday evening, Russian frontier guard press bureau informed 
ITAR-TASS today. 
  Meeting a decisive rebuff, the violators disappeared without 
an armed confrontation with frontier guards. 
  One day ago the third outpost of the Khorg frontier guard 
detachment came under automatic fire from Tajik territory. 
Russian frontier guards returned the fire. No casualties were 
reported among frontier guards. 

</TEXT>

