<H3> <TI>   Black Sea-Baltic League Conference Planned </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Black Sea-Baltic League Conference Planned </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1306092394 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 
1800 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1306092394 </F>
<F P=104>  Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service </F>
<F P=105>  Ukrainian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A meeting of the committee organizing an 
international conference of political parties from the countries 
of the so-called Black Sea-Baltic area was held in Kiev. It has 
already been reported that this conference is being called on 
the initiative of the Ukrainian Republican Party, the Democratic 
Party [of Ukraine], and the Green Party [of Ukraine] with the 
aim of setting up a league of political organizations of the 
countries between the [Black and Baltic] seas. In particular, 
it was stated at the meeting that the Belarusian Popular Front 
and a number of parties from Lithuania, Latvia, Estonia, 
Moldova, Romania, and Hungary have already expressed a desire to 
take part in the conference. 

</TEXT>

