<F P=102> LD1306074594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0719 GMT 13 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1306074594 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [By ITAR-TASS] </F>
  [Text] Moscow June 13 TASS -- The Russia's Democratic 
Choice Party has voted in favour of economist Yegor Gaydar being 
party chairman and Oleg Boyko, head of the National Credit Bank 
and chief of the Olby concern, chairman of the party's executive 
committee. 
  Boyko promised to contribute to creating an efficient 
organizational structure attracting more entrepreneurs to its 
ranks and boosting the party's publicity activity. 

</TEXT>

